tion`\n- `Timeout`\n- `HGET`\n\n### 共同故障源分析\n从两个服务 (`cartservice` 和 `frontend`) 的日志来看，它们都无法访问 `redis-cart` 导致超时异常。因此，这可能指向 `redis-cart` 服务出现性能瓶颈或网络问题。尽管 `cartservice` 单独也出现了一个 Kestrel 服务器警告，这在当前分析中不是主要问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"RedisTimeoutException\", \"Timeout\", \"HGET\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis cart storage timeout leading to service failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs from cartservice and frontend show RedisTimeoutException when accessing cart storage.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请根据上述分析确认 redis-cart 组件的配置和性能是否正常，以及网络是否存在延迟或其他问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "数据已成功加载，现在开始分析异常调用链和根因。\n\n### 分析结果\n以下是故障时间段内的显著异常指标及主要受影响的组件:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate exhibit a peak utilization from normal median 21.63% to fault P99 peak at 76.65%, affecting multiple dependent Pods.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Fault P99 of node_cpu_usage_rate reached 76.65% while normal was at 25.0%. Pods affected include: [currencyservice-2, checkoutservice-1, cartservice-2, adservice-2, paymentservice-0, redis-cart-0, recommendationservice-0, productcatalogservice-0, frontend-2].\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service rrt_max spikes from a normal median of 1807ms to a fault P99 of 63312ms.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Performance degradation indicates paymentservice-2 faced critical response time issues, associated with elevated rrt_max and rrt metrics.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod_cpu_usage variation suggests abnormal resource consumption patterns during the fault window.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod recommendationservice-0's cpu usage exhibited a notable increase with fault P99 reaching 0.06 compared to the normal value 0.01.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n根据指标发现可能的瓶颈，在以下部分展开进一步分析:\n1. 节点 `aiops-k8s-08` 的 CPU 资源可能是关键问题的根源。\n2. 是否 `paymentservice-2` 服务的资源配置需要优化，或请求过载需平衡。\n3. 可进一步跟踪 `recommendationservice` 的资源调度方式，查找异常负载原因。\n\n需要更多细化分析时，请查询相关服务日志及节点级别的资源分布状况。", "trace_analysis_findings": "已完成数据采集，现在进行初步分析识别异常调用链。\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"recommendationservice-0->productcatalogservice-0\",\n    \"frontend-1->recommendationservice-0\",\n    \"checkoutservice-2->cartservice-2\",\n    \"frontend-0->cartservice-0\",\n    \"checkoutservice-2->shippingservice-2\",\n    \"frontend-2->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend-2->productcatalogservice-0\",\n    \"frontend-1->currencyservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend/RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1到recommendationservice-0，延迟从4130ms上升到3659ms，发生18次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService/Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis调用耗时显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis耗时+slow增加;Total Debug pg fails\"\n    }\n```\n"}
